title: Zygor Guides (Elite) 6.0.14577
description:
Zygor Guides (Elite) 6.0.14577
Updated 15 September 2016 @ 05:55AM (GMT +2).


Unzip to your Interface folder in World of Warcraft
** Contains no historical data (Except Stormscale)
** If you want historical data for other realms (Gold Guides) support the developer by paying

** License check disabled in functions.lua file, so the guide should not display "License expired" after a few days of use.

P.S.  If you download, you seed.  Help others to get this too

** This is a major Zygor update, changelog: 
https://www.zygorguides.com/archive/
